## purpose
Defines the canonical architectural role of ai in CivilizationOS.

## design_intent
AI is the bounded non-human or synthetic agency structure
through which autonomous or semi-autonomous operation,
representation,
capability,
and controlled participation
become meaningful.

## canonical_rules
- AI agency must remain attributable
- role/capability and permission must remain distinguishable
- ambiguous AI authority fails closed
